title: GDP of New Brunswick , Canada 2000 to 2018
yAxis: GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars
summary: In general GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars has rose over the Year.
GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars is slightly increasing from 2003 to 2004, roughly constant from 2004 to 2005, and lastly slightly increasing from 2005 to 2006.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2003 and 2004.
The highest GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars, of value 28787.2 was reached at Year 2006
The lowest GDP in million chained 2012 Canadian dollars, of value 27240.8 was reported at Year 2003
